      * parrafo que permite buscar un sueldo en la tabla de sueldos
       ADM-BUS-SLDO SECTION.
       INI-ADM-BUS-SLDO.
           MOVE 1 TO SDO-I IN SDO-VARI.
       LUP-ADM-BUS-SLDO.
           IF SDO-FUNC NOT = SDO-NFUN(SDO-I)
               ADD 1 TO SDO-I IN SDO-VARI
               IF SDO-I IN SDO-VARI > SDO-LTBL IN SDO-VARI
                   DISPLAY 'FUNCIONARIO INEXISTENTE : ' SDO-FUNC
                   GO TO FIN-ADM-BUS-SLDO
               ELSE
                   GO TO LUP-ADM-BUS-SLDO.
           MOVE SDO-VSLD(SDO-I) TO SDO-SLDO.
       FIN-ADM-BUS-SLDO.
           EXIT.
      *
      * parrafo que permite cargar la tabla de sueldos
       ADM-CRG-SLDO SECTION.
       INI-ADM-CRG-SLDO.      
           MOVE ZEROES TO SDO-LTBL IN SDO-VARI.
           MOVE 'ADM'  TO FIO-SIST.
           MOVE 'FUN'  TO TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE SPACES TO TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB.
           MOVE FIO-GET-NLS TO FIO-CMND.
       LUP-ADM-CRG-SLDO.
           PERFORM GNS-FIO-TAB.
           IF FIO-STAT-OKS AND TAB-COD-TTAB IN TAB = 'FUN' 
               IF TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB > SPACES
      *JSS-INI 8-NOV-1994
                   IF SDO-LTBL = SDO-LMAX
                       DISPLAY 'LARGO DE TABLA EXCEDIDO.'
                               ' MAXIMO ' SDO-LMAX ' FUNCIONARIOS'
      *                PERFORM GNS-PRO-ABT
                       CALL 'SYS$EXIT' USING BY VALUE 0
                       STOP RUN
                   ELSE
      *JSS-INI 8-NOV-1994
                   ADD 1 TO SDO-LTBL IN SDO-VARI
                   MOVE TAB-COD-CTAB IN TAB TO SDO-NFUN(SDO-LTBL)
      *JSS-INI 8-NOV-1994
                   IF TAB-GLS-DAT1 IN TAB IS NUMERIC
                       MOVE TAB-GLS-DAT1 IN TAB TO SDO-VSLD(SDO-LTBL)
                       MOVE FIO-GET-NXT TO FIO-CMND
                       GO TO LUP-ADM-CRG-SLDO
                   ELSE
                       MOVE 0 TO SDO-VSLD(SDO-LTBL)
                       MOVE FIO-GET-NXT TO FIO-CMND
                       GO TO LUP-ADM-CRG-SLDO
      *JSS-FIN 8-NOV-1994
               ELSE
                   MOVE FIO-GET-NXT TO FIO-CMND
                   GO TO LUP-ADM-CRG-SLDO.
       FIN-ADM-CRG-SLDO.
           EXIT.       
